org.eclipse.emf.compare

Interface ResourceLocationChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Diff, EObject, Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResourceLocationChangeImpl, ResourceLocationChangeSpec

    public interface ResourceLocationChange
extends Diff
    A representation of the model object 'Resource Location Change'. This particular kind of difference describes the change of a resource's location.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Location
    • Changed Location

    Since:
    3.2
